5... a6 6. Bxc4 b5 7. Bb3 { this is the most challenging retreat for Black. }
7... Bb7 { Black develops the bishop and intends to play ...c5. } 8. O-O c5 9.
e4 { An interesting pawn sacrifice that has been quite popular lately. } 9...
cxd4 10. Nxd4 Nc6
