{ With this move we enter the Colle-Zukertort system. In this chapter, we are mainly going to analyse two of White's most prominent setups.   Set-up 1@@EndBracket@@ When White plays c2-c3, Bf1-d3 and Nb1-d2.   Set-up 2@@EndBracket@@ When he fianchetto's his dark-squared bishop with b2-b3 and Bc1-b2. }
