{ two white pieces, the bishop on g5 and the knight on c3, are attacked and there is no way that white escapes from this double attack. }
11. Nxd4 Bxc3 12. Nxc6 { Now Black has the nice move, } 12... fxg5
{ using the pin on the knight on c6. } 13. bxc3
{ 13.Qa3  Qf6  14.Rxd7  Kxd7  15.bxc3  Qf4+  16.Kb2  Qxf2+  and Black is winning.  17.Ka1  Qe1+  18.Kb2  bxc6  0-1 @@StartBracket@@18@@EndBracket@@ Londyn,R @@StartBracket@@2401@@EndBracket@@-Kobo,O @@StartBracket@@2490@@EndBracket@@ Teplice CZE 2016. }
