{ White has managed to regain the pawn, but the position is still very concrete with tactical ideas. }
18. Na5 Qxe4
{ Black grabs the e4-pawn exploiting the fact that the d7-knight is taboo. }
19. Qd6+ Kg7 20. Rxb8 Nxb8 21. Qg3+ Qg6 22. Qc7
{ White wants to grab the a7-pawn after which his active pieces may give him some chances for an initiative. So, it is time to activate our own knight with, }
22... Na6 23. Qd6
