23... Nb8 24. Qc7 Na6
{ and the game ended in a draw. ½-½ @@StartBracket@@26@@EndBracket@@ Ipatov,A @@StartBracket@@2650@@EndBracket@@-Van Foreest,J @@StartBracket@@2622@@EndBracket@@ Saint Louis USA 2019 }
