8... Be7 9. O-O O-O 10. b3
{ 10.Nc3  Nbd7  11.Re1  hoping to create some pressure down the e-file. We continue our plan,   11.b3  Nb6  12.Bb2  transposes  11...Nb6  12.b3  Re8  Black gets ready to neutralize the pressure on the e-file. Now after,  13.Bb2  Nxc4   13...Bf8  1/2-1/2 @@StartBracket@@21@@EndBracket@@ Loifenfeld, J @@StartBracket@@2413@@EndBracket@@ -Scheider, J @@StartBracket@@2306@@EndBracket@@ Germany 2018  14.Nxc4  Ba6  we transpose to the mainline. }
