Ne2 Bg7 8. O-O O-O 9. Nec3
{ White wants to put one knight on c3, hoping to manoeuvre the other knight to c4 in the future. }
9... Nbd7 10. Be2 { White frees the c4 square for the b1-knight. } 10... Ne8
