{ Benko Declined 5.b6 @@StartSquare@@GM Swapnil, Dhopade@@EndSquare@@ } 18...
cxb4 19. Be3 c5
{ Black has managed to rectify his crooked pawns while still maintaining some pressure on the queenside. He has ideas like ...Rb5 followed by ...Ra5 with a slightly better position. Grochowalski,P @@StartBracket@@2062@@EndBracket@@-Chapman,T @@StartBracket@@2249@@EndBracket@@ London 2010 }
