d5 2. Nc3 Nf6 3. Bg5 c5 4. Bxf6 gxf6 5. e4 dxe4 6. dxc5 f5 7. Qxd8+ Kxd8 8.
O-O-O+ Nd7 { 8...Bd7  is the recommendation in our repertoire. } 9. g4
